name: Tribe Elders ~ Nana Dara
description:
"Blessed is the pure in heart".
And Blessed is the great Nana.
The last remaining of her kind.
The reader of leaves and entrails.
And in her wisdom she sees great prosperity across the land.
The Ancestors have confirmed the omens are good and the knowledge to be shared.
She prayed long and hard for moments like these.
Since imparting her knowledge on the 7 Talisman of the Work to the wise, she has decided to offer little or no more.
She wants to see her kin thrive.
She wishes to see them all succeed.
She has cast the kernels of gold amongst her children and now she watches them feed with joy.
Blessed are the pure.
Blessed are the just.
She brings her blessings to the sinful too, so they may finally see they are sinless after all.
